Position: Software Engineer at SunTec Business Solutions.  
• Transaction Business Management System (TBMS) is a state-of-the-art convergent billing solution for transaction based business introduced by SunTec. The system has been structured in a modular configuration to enable easy customization for network application. The reliability and flexibility of TBMS gives its users the power to adapt to changing requirements and effectively manage customers, services and revenues in real time. It supports true convergence across heterogeneous networks and services, and allows seamless interaction with external systems, through the well documented APIs. The product is built around the distributed ORACLE relational database. The major modules of TBMS include Billing, Pricing (Rating), Consolidation, Mediation and Customer Care.  
◦ Mediation Module in TBMS: Collects the data from input records, perform necessary validations, data enrichment's, convert them to a normalized output format and pass them on to downstream applications for Pricing and Billing. This module includes collection and validation of transaction records, Aggregation of partial transaction records, Format change and record normalization and Business transformation of data.  
◦ Consolidation Module in TBMS: Consolidates the transformed records after Mediation process, based on the configured criteria before sending the records to rating systems. Also can be used for multi-level consolidation of records after rating.  
◦ Pricing Module in TBMS: Provides a complete solution for pricing any transaction based system, capble of providing a centralized fee management infrastructure. It is a high performance Relationship Based Transaction Pricing engine.  
◦ Customer Care Module in TBMS: Provides the web based interface to record and maintain customer data. This modules has all the reports needed for customer management.  
  
Programming Language/Technologies: Java and C++

In this class, you will learn about the most effective machine learning techniques, and gain practice implementing them and geting them to work for yourself. More importantly, you'll learn about not only the theoretical underpinnings of learning, but also gain the practical know-how needed to quickly and powerfully apply these techniques to new problems. As the solutions inherently require to combine visual and natural language processing with abstract reasoning, the problem is considered as AI-complete.
